{"tid":1150992,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【母親節收大肚寫真】四太梁安琪負責幫孫女改名：荷包蛋或荷葉飯","createTime":"2019-05-12T09:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T09:47:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4149f9726660973106105429e4986fe68ba30c95","tid":1150992,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:10:16.000Z","msg":"賭王四房長女何超盈早前去了美國，陪哈佛學霸未婚夫辛奇隆（Thomas）兼安胎，日前已返港，今日在IG貼了大肚寫真，作為送給四太梁安琪的母親節禮物，並公佈腹中是B女，還替她改了花名「荷包蛋」。（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PW3Eui\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PW3Eui&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=13c115c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PW3Eui</a> ）<br />\n《蘋果》今日聯絡準婆婆四太，問到母親節收有心思的禮物心情，她笑言：「之前影完，都唔知佢會今日擺上網，當然開心啦，佢哋都係啱啱喺美國返嚟幾日，一齊過母親節。」問到她抱孫女的心情，四太表示：「仔又好，女又好，我都一樣開心。」提到孫女已有花名「荷包蛋」，四太說：「荷同何個音一樣，佢哋細個時，個個都有花名，大家一齊諗，想諗過搞笑啲名，咪叫食物，一係叫荷包蛋，一係叫荷葉飯，都係開玩笑。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190512/large/1557638489_c99d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190512%2Flarge%2F1557638489_c99d.jpg&h=a7b12cfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190512/large/1557638489_f1fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190512%2Flarge%2F1557638489_f1fe.jpg&h=a4704e72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190512/large/1557638692_cb57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190512%2Flarge%2F1557638692_cb57.jpg&h=0998b937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190512/large/1557638692_ca6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190512%2Flarge%2F1557638692_ca6a.jpg&h=486bc4b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br